    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a medium-sized pot with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong>, <strong>crushed garlic </strong>and <strong>chilli halves </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pot</p><p>Cook for 6-7 min or until the vegetables are starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
