    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim the green stalk[s] off your<strong> aubergine[s]</strong> and chop lengthways into wedges</p><p>Add the<strong> aubergine wedges</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until the wedges are tender and golden</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
