    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely, then chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Cut your <strong>avocado[s]</strong> in half lengthways, around the<strong> stone[s]</strong></p><p>Remove the <strong>stone[s] </strong>using a spoon, then scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh</strong> and dice roughly</p>",
