    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> diced avocado</strong>, <strong>chopped tomato </strong>and<strong> </strong>most of the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>(save some for garnish!) in a bowl</p><p>Add the<strong> </strong>juice of<strong> half </strong>your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lime[s] </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong>, then give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>avocado salsa</strong></p>",
