    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p><p>Serve the <strong>Mexican-style adobo sauce</strong> with the <strong>roasted aubergine wedges</strong> on top<strong> </strong>and the <strong>cooked rice</strong> and <strong>avocado salsa </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped coriander </strong>and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
